            "title": "BRANITELJICE PROSLAVILE DAN ŽENA",
            "summary": "Povodom Međunarodnog dana žena, u nedjelju 8.ožujka 2026 godine, članice Kluba žena Udruge dragovoljaca i&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Povodom Međunarodnog dana žena, u nedjelju 8.ožujka 2026 godine, članice Kluba žena Udruge dragovoljaca i veterana Domovinskog rata RH Podružnice Splitsko dalmatinske županije, organizirale su u prostoru Alkarskih dvora u Sinju druženje braniteljica, uz glazbu u živo i prikladnu večeru. Uz ugodnu atmosferu i posebnog gosta gradonačelnika Sinja Miru Bulja svečanost je trajala do kasnih večernjih sati.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/1-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x1440\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/1-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/2-2.jpg\" data-size=\"641x610\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/2-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"641\" height=\"610\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/3-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x1440\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/3-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/4-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/4-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/5-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/5-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/95/gallery/6-2.jpg\" data-size