        {
            "id": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/radovi-na-lovackom-domu.html",
            "url": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/radovi-na-lovackom-domu.html",
            "title": "RADOVI NA LOVAČKOM DOMU",
            "summary": "Dana 8.03 2026 godine, članovi UDVDR RH PSDŽ i članovi LU Ljubljan nastavili su sa&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Dana 8.03 2026 godine, članovi UDVDR RH PSDŽ i članovi LU Ljubljan nastavili su sa radnim akcijama, postavljanja novog krova na Lovačkom Domu u Dugopolju.</p>\n<p>Ovo je  nastavak radova koji su započeli prošle godine, kad je cijeli objekt obložen panel pločama, a sada se sa istima postavlja krov doma. Lovci su kao i uvijek pripremili lovački ručak  za sve sudionike. Naša UDVDR SDZ u tijeku godine koristi prostor ovog objekta za svoje aktivnosti: od održavanja sjednica Skupštine, druženja dragovoljaca i veterana povodom obljetnica iz Domovinskog rata, organiziranja, sportskih, kulturnih aktivnosti.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/1.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/1-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/2.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/3.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x1440\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/4.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/4-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/5.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/5-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/6.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x1440\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/6-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/7.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/7-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/8.jpg\" data-size=\"1440x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/8-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/9.jpg\" data-size=\"811x1440\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/9-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"1278\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/10.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/10-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/11.jpg\" data-size=\"1335x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/11-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/12.jpg\" data-size=\"1335x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/93/gallery/12-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
