        {
            "id": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/obilazak-muzeja-domovinskog-rata-u-dubrovniku.html",
            "url": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/obilazak-muzeja-domovinskog-rata-u-dubrovniku.html",
            "title": "OBILAZAK MUZEJA DOMOVINSKOG RATA U DUBROVNIKU",
            "summary": "Predstavnici UDVDR RH Podružnice Splitsko dalmatinske županije Ogranka Dugopolje posjetili su Muzej Domovinskog rata Dubrovnik&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Predstavnici UDVDR RH Podružnice Splitsko dalmatinske županije Ogranka Dugopolje posjetili su Muzej Domovinskog rata Dubrovnik u tvrđavi Imperijal na Srđu. U društvu s ravnateljiucom muzeja Varinom Turk obišli su izložbene eksponate sa slikama i popratnim testovma o događajima pa vrijeme Domovinskog rata na području Dubrovnika i južnog dijela bojišta.Kao partneri muzeja Prošle godine smo u Dugopolju postavili izložbu „Dani ponosa 1” o herojskoj obrani Dubrovnika 1991 a ove godine ćemo također postaviti izložbu „Dani ponosa 2” o oslobađanju Dubrovnika i Dubrovačkog kraja 1992.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/1.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/1-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/2.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/3.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/4.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/4-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/5.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/5-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/6.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/6-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/7.jpg\" data-size=\"751x1001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/91/gallery/7-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
