        {
            "id": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/33-obljetnica-vro-maslenica.html",
            "url": "https://udvdrpsdz.hr/33-obljetnica-vro-maslenica.html",
            "title": "33 OBLJETNICA VRO MASLENICA",
            "summary": "Trideset i treću obljetnicu vojno-redarstvene operacije Maslenica Predstavnici UDVDR RH PSDŽ obilježili su sa više&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Trideset i treću obljetnicu vojno-redarstvene operacije Maslenica Predstavnici UDVDR RH PSDŽ obilježili su sa više događanja, od 17. siječnja do 22. siječnja 2026. U Subotu 17 01 2026 desetak naših članica Kluba žena UDVDR SDŽ sudjelovalo je na Molitvenoj hodnji Koracima nade u istinu; Zeleni hrast - Kašić - Paljuv – Pridraga. Na putu dugom  25 km zaustavljale su se na svim spomen obilježjima i zapalili svijeće i pomolili se za poginule branitelje.</p>\n<p>U srijedu 21. 01 u sklopu centralne proslavi u Zadru, položili smo vijenac i zapalili svijeće na spomen obilježje 3. bojne Imotski sokolovi 4. gardijske brigade Pauci Ulica Ante Starčevića, Zadar, dok su treći dan 22.01 2025 položili vijenac i zapalili svijeće na spomen obilježju 3. gardijske brigade Kune; Kašić i na spomen obilježju 4. gardijske brigade Pauci; Islam Latinski gdje su položili vijence kod spomen obilježja križa za sve hrvatske branitelje poginule u VRO Maslenica ’93.; Maslenički most, zaštitni pojas DC 8, Prisustvovali su svetoj misi u crkvi Marije zaštitnice kršćana, u Paljuvu.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/1-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1077x794\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/1-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"531\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/2-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1063x797\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/2-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/3-3.jpg\" data-size=\"900x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/3-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/4-3.jpg\" data-size=\"900x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/4-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/5-3.jpg\" data-size=\"724x479\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/5-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"476\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/6-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1060x458\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/6-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"311\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/7-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1079x808\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/7-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"539\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/8-3.jpg\" data-size=\"900x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/8-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/9-3.jpg\" data-size=\"906x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/9-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"954\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/10-3.jpg\" data-size=\"900x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/10-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/11-3.jpg\" data-size=\"900x1200\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/11-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/12-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x803\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://udvdrpsdz.hr/media/posts/87/gallery/12-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"535\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
